history_english:
Bambini Crostini is an Italian Brainrot created by TikTok user @top.brainrot on the 15th of March, 2025.

Bambini Crostini is an absurd and iconic figure from the Italian Brainrot universe. As the name suggests, the character combines the childish (“bambini”) with a croissant-like shape (“crostini”).

In the picture, Bambini Crostini is seen as a brown deer with a childish face and a body reminiscent of a crispy croissant. Her eyes stare into nothingness, and the whole thing exudes a strange mix of cuteness and disturbing energy – classic Brainrot.
history_spanish:
Bambini Crostini es un Italian Brainrot creado por el usuario de TikTok @top.brainrot el 15 de marzo de 2025.

Bambini Crostini es una figura absurda e iconica del universo Italian Brainrot. Como sugiere el nombre, el personaje combina lo infantil (“bambini”) con una forma similar a un croissant (“crostini”).

En la imagen, Bambini Crostini aparece como un ciervo marron con un rostro infantil y un cuerpo que recuerda a un croissant crujiente. Sus ojos miran al vacio y en conjunto transmite una extrana mezcla de ternura y energia inquietante, un sello clasico del Brainrot.

lyrics_english: Blueberrinni Octopussini. Bloop, bloop, bloop, octopussi. This little animal lives on the seabed and enjoys its sweet life. Good girl, respect.
lyrics_spanish: Blueberrinni Octopussini. Bloop, bloop, bloop, octopussi. Este pequeno animal vive en el lecho marino y disfruta de su dulce vida. Buena chica, respeto.
personality_english:
She is an octopus with a hairy blueberry as a head, residing on the ocean floor among coral reefs and other blueberries.

She is the wife of Tralalero Tralala.

Es un pulpo que tiene como cabeza una arandano peludo, y habita el fondo del oceano entre arrecifes de coral y otras arandanos.  

Es la esposa de Tralalero Tralala.
history_english: Blueberrinni Octopussini is an Italian Brainrot character created by @alexey_pigeon on March 10th, 2025.
history_spanish: Blueberrinni Octopussini es un personaje de Italian Brainrot creado por @alexey_pigeon el 10 de marzo de 2025.
inbattle_english: Blueberrini is typically deployed ahead of main forces for psychological softening, environmental sabotage, and underwater intel gathering. Ideal for asymmetric warfare, hostage rescues, or operations requiring zero visible violence but maximum effectiveness.

name: Glorbo Fruttodrillo
lyrics_italian: Glorbo Fruttodrillo nel profondo della Palude glorbo fruttodrillo regnava il suo corpo era un'enorme anguria a strisce ma la testa e la coda tutto alligatoreLe creature sussurravano del suo morso letale e della sua polpa succosa. Alcuni volevano essere suoi amici, altri volevano assaggiarlo.Un giorno un cacciatore sciocco arrivo con un coltello. “Un cocomero che cammina… jackpot.” Glorbo sorrise. *Chomp.* Quella notte, la palude rimase in silenzio.
lyrics_english: Glorbo Fruttodrillo deep in the Swamp glorbo fruttodrillo reigned his body was a huge striped watermelon but his head and tail all alligator! The creatures whispered of his deadly bite and his juicy flesh. Some wanted to be his friend, some wanted to taste him. One day a foolish hunter came with a knife. “A walking watermelon… jackpot.” Glorbo smiled, CHOMP. That night, the swamp was silent.
lyrics_spanish: Glorbo Fruttodrillo en lo profundo del pantano reinaba Glorbo Fruttodrillo, cuyo cuerpo era una enorme sandia rayada, pero cuya cabeza y cola eran de caiman. Las criaturas susurraban sobre su mordedura letal y su jugosa pulpa. Algunos querian ser sus amigos, otros querian probarlo. Un dia, un cazador tonto llego con un cuchillo. «Una sandia que camina... ¡bingo!». Glorbo sonrio. *Mordisco.* Esa noche, el pantano permanecio en silencio.
personality_english: Glorbo Fruttodrillo is an anomaly in the form of a large watermelon, however it has the head and limbs of an Alligator/crocodile. He is standing in the dense jungle.
personality_spanish: Glorbo Fruttodrillo es una anomalia con forma de gran sandia; sin embargo, tiene la cabeza y las extremidades de un caiman/cocodrilo. Esta de pie en la densa jungla.
history_english: Glorbo Fruttodrillo is one of many italian brainrot animals Created by Egggr. The original image depicts a alligator with the body of a watermelon, this creature presumably inspired other creators to make their own watermelon-themed characters.
history_spanish: Glorbo Fruttodrillo es uno de los muchos animales brainrot italianos creados por Egggr. La imagen original muestra un caiman con cuerpo de sandia; esta criatura presumiblemente inspiro a otros creadores a hacer sus propios personajes tematicos de sandia.
inbattle_english: Glorbo Fruttodrillo can fare decently against smaller/weaker characters, however as seen in his fight with Tung Tung Tung Sahur, a more powerful character, he seems to lose very badly. (Glorbo got exploded as Tung Sahur exploded from the inside of him) Glorbo Fruttodrillo can beat most characters with his powers especially the more smaller characters he has seed bombs he can launch explosive watermelon seeds with sniper level precision so it takes a lot of damage then he also has solar beam he can do that ability it’s where he absorbs sunlight through his rind and fires a concentrated energy blast it’s basically a fruit powered laser but if the other opponent hurts Glorbo Fruttodrillo he can regenerate by growing new fruits from his own body.
inbattle_spanish: Glorbo Fruttodrillo puede enfrentarse decentemente a personajes mas pequenos o debiles; sin embargo, como se vio en su pelea con Tung Tung Tung Sahur, un personaje mas poderoso, parece perder muy mal. (Glorbo exploto cuando Tung Sahur exploto desde dentro de el). Glorbo Fruttodrillo puede vencer a la mayoria de los personajes con sus poderes, especialmente a los mas pequenos; tiene bombas de semillas y puede lanzar semillas explosivas de sandia con precision de francotirador, lo que causa mucho dano. Tambien tiene el rayo solar: puede absorber la luz del sol a traves de su corteza y disparar una rafaga de energia concentrada, basicamente un laser alimentado por fruta. Si el oponente hiere a Glorbo Fruttodrillo, puede regenerarse haciendo crecer nuevas frutas de su propio cuerpo.

name: Ballerina Cappuccina
lyrics_italian:
Ballerina Cappuccina, mi mi mi mi!
E la moglie di Cappuccino Assassino.
E ama la musica, la la la la!
La sua passione e il Ballerino Lololo.
lyrics_english:
Ballerina Cappuccina, mi mi mi mi!
She is the wife of Cappuccino Assassino.
And she loves music, la la la la!
Her passion is Ballerino Lololo.
lyrics_spanish:
Bailarina Cappuccina, mi mi mi mi!
Ella es la esposa de Cappuccino Assassino.
Y ama la musica, la la la la!
Su pasion es Ballerino Lololo.
personality_english:
Her rival is Espressona Signora, who seduced her husband, Cappuccino Assassino.
Despite being married, she is often depicted in love with (cheating with) Tung Tung Tung Sahur. This doesn't count as something canon since her creator didn't pair her with him, but with her husband, Capuccino Assasino.
Both Ballerina Nicotina and Icharinna Matchanova have a rivalry with Ballerina Cappuccina although these two said rivalries seem to be one sided.
There are a few Candle Cove headcanons based around the idea that the show's world is the same as Italian Brainrot's universe with one said fan headcanons being that Ballerina Cappuccina is the secret identity of Hoody Hans (a villain in the show's first season) via some The Mask style shenanigans involving "his" yellow cloak.
personality_spanish:
Su rival es Espressona Signora, quien sedujo a su esposo, Cappuccino Assassino.  
A pesar de estar casada, a menudo se la representa enamorada (enganando) con Tung Tung Tung Sahur. Esto no cuenta como algo canonico, ya que su creador no la emparejo con el, sino con su esposo, Cappuccino Assassino.  
Tanto Ballerina Nicotina como Icharinna Matchanova tienen una rivalidad con Ballerina Cappuccina, aunque ambas rivalidades parecen ser unilaterales.  
Existen algunos headcanons de *Candle Cove* basados en la idea de que el mundo del show es el mismo que el del universo de Italian Brainrot, con uno de esos headcanons diciendo que Ballerina Cappuccina es la identidad secreta de Hoody Hans (un villano de la primera temporada del show), a traves de un truco al estilo de *La Mascara* que involucra su capa amarilla.
history_english: Ballerina Cappuccina is an Italian brainrot character introduced on the 19th of March, 2025 by TikTok user @aironicfun. She is a human ballerina with a coffee mug as her head. She is the wife of Cappuccino Assassino. She can usually be seen dancing or singing. In an older iteration of the meme, she could be seen pirouetting gracefully. She is one of the first Italian brainrots.
history_spanish: Ballerina Cappuccina es un personaje de Italian Brainrot introducido el 19 de marzo de 2025 por el usuario de TikTok @aironicfun. Es una bailarina humana con una taza de cafe como cabeza. Es la esposa de Cappuccino Assassino. Usualmente se la puede ver bailando o cantando. En una version mas antigua del meme, se la veia haciendo piruetas con gracia. Es uno de los primeros brainrots italianos.
reception_english: Ballerina Cappuccina sits among the most well-known characters of Italian Brainrot, with the most popular video having reached over 50 million views on TikTok. Many stories and additional characters (including characters like Espressona Signora and Ballerino Lololo) have been created thanks to her.
reception_spanish: Ballerina Cappuccina se encuentra entre los personajes mas reconocidos de Italian Brainrot, con su video mas popular superando los 50 millones de vistas en TikTok. Gracias a ella se han creado muchas historias y personajes adicionales (incluyendo a Espressona Signora y Ballerino Lololo).

name: Bobrito bandito
lyrics_italian: Oi, oi, oi! Bobrito Bandito? El Bobrito Gangsterito! Banditelli Don Bobrelli! El Bandito Bobrito Gangsterito... Bobrito Bandito?
lyrics_english: Oi, oi, oi! Bobrito Bandito? El Bobrito Gangsterito! Banditelli Don Bobrelli! El Bandito Bobrito Gangsterito... Bobrito Bandito?
lyrics_spanish: Oi, oi, oi! Bobrito Bandito? El Bobrito Gangsterito! Banditelli Don Bobrelli! El Bandito Bobrito Gangsterito... Bobrito Bandito?
personality_english: Bobrito Bandito is an anthropomorphic Beaver in the form of a bandit/mafia member. He wears an orange-brown coloured trench coat with a suit and tie underneath, and he wears a fedora on top. Bobrito Bandito is often seen carrying around a Thompson Submachine Gun (Tommy Gun) with him, as well as smoking into the dark, cold night. He somewhat resembles a mafia/gangster from 1910-40. Some people think he is a bear, which is incorrect.
personality_spanish: Bobrito Bandito es un castor antropomorfico con forma de bandido/mafioso. Viste una gabardina de color naranja-marron con traje y corbata debajo, y un sombrero fedora encima. A menudo se le ve cargando una metralleta Thompson (Tommy Gun), ademas de fumar en la noche oscura y fria. Se asemeja un poco a un mafioso/ganster de 1910-1940. Algunos piensan que es un oso, lo cual es incorrecto.
history_english: Bobrito Bandito is a mafia beaver with a gun and smoking cannabis and he also pilots Bombardini Goatini.
history_spanish: Bobrito Bandito es un castor de la mafia con una pistola y fumando cannabis y tambien pilota Bombardini Goatini.
inbattle_english: Bobrito Bandito is an exceptional reconnaissance fighter specializing in stealth. He is often seen in battles appearing out of his opponent's shadows, then switfly assassinating them. However, his weakness lies in direct confrontation, as his build heavily lacks defense.
inbattle_spanish: Bobrito Bandito es un excepcional luchador de reconocimiento especializado en sigilo. A menudo se le ve en batallas surgiendo de las sombras de sus oponentes y asesinandolos con rapidez. Sin embargo, su debilidad reside en el enfrentamiento directo, ya que su complexion carece de defensa.

name: Bri Bri Bicus Dicus
lyrics_italian: Bri Bri Bicus Dicus de Bicus de Dicus, un dannato uccello volante che marcia per le strade di Roma, rimproverando chiunque, a suo avviso, disonori l'Impero. Non crede nei valori moderni e rimpiange il vecchio ordine.
lyrics_english: Bri Bri Bicus Dicus de Bicus de Dicus, a damned flying bird who marches through the streets of Rome, berating anyone who, in his opinion, dishonors the Empire. He does not believe in modern values ​​and longs for the old order.
lyrics_spanish: Bri Bri Bicus Dicus de Bicus de Dicus, un maldito pajaro volador que marcha por las calles de Roma, reprendiendo a cualquiera que, en su opinion, deshonre al Imperio. No cree en los valores modernos y anora el viejo orden.
personality_english: Shouting at clouds is one of his favourite pastimes. Also, it is said that he won his raspberry necklace after slaying one of Brr Brr Patapim's ancient ancestors, who was bearing fruit at the time. The berries grow back once eaten.
personality_spanish: Gritarle a las nubes es uno de sus pasatiempos favoritos. Tambien se dice que gano su collar de frambuesas despues de derrotar a uno de los antiguos ancestros de Brr Brr Patapim, quien en ese momento portaba frutos. Las bayas vuelven a crecer una vez que se comen.
history_english:
Bri Bri Bicus Dicus De Bicus De Dicus is a bird with a raspberry necklace, gold and red gladiator armor and a cape in front of the Colosseum. He has human feet in sandals instead of penguin feet. In the original video, the song "The Sound of Your Fear" plays. Bri Bri Bicus Dicus De Bicus De Dicus is more of a historically oriented character in the Italian Brainrot universe, combining avian characteristics with Roman imperial aesthetics and an unusual raspberry necklace. This fusion creates a fascinating character that mixes both ancient militarism and natural peculiarity.

The name is a reference to the centurion 'Biggus Dickus' from the film 'Life of Brian'.
history_spanish:
Bri Bri Bicus Dicus De Bicus De Dicus es un ave con un collar de frambuesas, armadura de gladiador dorada y roja, y una capa frente al Coliseo. Tiene pies humanos con sandalias en lugar de patas de pinguino. En el video original, suena la cancion "The Sound of Your Fear". Bri Bri Bicus Dicus De Bicus De Dicus es un personaje mas orientado a lo historico dentro del universo Italian Brainrot, combinando caracteristicas aviares con la estetica imperial romana y un inusual collar de frambuesas. Esta fusion crea un personaje fascinante que mezcla tanto el militarismo antiguo como una peculiaridad natural.

El nombre es una referencia al centurion 'Biggus Dickus' de la pelicula 'La vida de Brian'.
inbattle_english: During the Croco-Avian Wars, Brri Brri Bicus Dicus sided with the avians and returned to Rome a hero, an icon of Rome's glorious past.
inbattle_spanish: Durante las Guerras Croco-Aviar, Bri Bri Bicus Dicus se puso del lado de las aves y regreso a Roma como un heroe, un icono del glorioso pasado de Roma.

name: Boneca ambalabu
lyrics_italian: Boneca Ambalabu. L'entita malvagia che sta ultimamente turbando la societa, fa si che gli scienziati riflettano a lungo su come affrontarla. Uno di loro e un famoso scienziato a riflettere attentamente per trovare un modo per affrontarla. Uno dei piu famosi scienziati, il Prof. Rusdi, ha rivelato i risultati delle sue ricerche su questo Boneca Ambalabu. In un breve video, prima che venisse dichiarato scomparso, ha spiegato che l'unico modo per salvarsi quando si incontra Ambalabu direttamente e il nulla. Ha sottolineato che non c'e modo di contrastare il Boneca Ambalabu. L'unica cosa che puoi fare e correre il piu velocemente possibile e non voltarti mai indietro. Finora, nessuno scienziato e stato in grado di svelare il mistero di questo Boneca Ambalabu.
lyrics_english: Boneca Ambalabu. The evil entity that has been disturbing society lately, makes scientists think hard to find a way to deal with it. One of them is a famous scientist, Prof. Rusdi, revealed the results of his research on this Boneca Ambalabu. In a short video before he was declared missing. It was explained that the only way to save yourself when meeting Ambalabu directly is nothing. He emphasized that there is no way to counter the Boneca Ambalabu. The only thing you can do is run as fast as you can And, never look back. Until now, no scientist has been able to reveal the mystery of this Boneca Ambalabu.
lyrics_spanish: Boneca Ambalabu. La entidad maligna que ha estado perturbando a la sociedad ultimamente ha hecho que los cientificos reflexionen sobre como lidiar con ella. Uno de ellos, el famoso cientifico Prof. Rusdi, revelo los resultados de su investigacion sobre este Boneca Ambalabu. En un breve video, antes de que fuera declarado desaparecido, explico que la unica forma de salvarse al encontrarse directamente con Ambalabu es nada. Enfatizo que no hay forma de contrarrestarlo. Lo unico que se puede hacer es correr tan rapido como se pueda y nunca mirar atras. Hasta ahora, ningun cientifico ha podido revelar el misterio de este Boneca Ambalabu.
personality_english:
Boneca Ambalabu (sometimes Boneka Ambalabu) is an Indonesian Brainrot character. It's one of the earliest characters, being created on the 2nd of February, 2025 by TikTok user @ofuscabreno.

It is an anomaly that has a car tire instead of a torso, a frog's head and human legs. It is shown in a daytime city environment, with cars and houses visible in the background. Despite its friendly and non-threatening appearance, it is an evil entity that terrorizes society.
personality_spanish:
Boneca Ambalabu (a veces Boneka Ambalabu) es un personaje indonesio de Brainrot. Es uno de los primeros personajes, creado el 2 de febrero de 2025 por el usuario de TikTok @ofuscabreno.

Es una anomalia que tiene una llanta de coche en lugar de torso, cabeza de rana y piernas humanas. Se muestra en un entorno urbano diurno, con coches y casas visibles al fondo. A pesar de su apariencia amigable y discreta, es una entidad maligna que aterroriza a la sociedad.
history_english:
The audio of Boneka Ambalabu is not original - it is taken from a video dating as far back as October 2024. The original video is part of a series about Boneka Ambalabu, who is a doll with the face of Dreamybull, a famous internet meme personality.
The name "Boneka Ambalabu" comes from a few words, the first being Boneka, which is Indonesian for "doll". "Ambalabu" is a mixture between "Ambatukam", a phrase often used in Dreamybull memes which were popular around 2022, and "Labubu", which is a doll made by the Chinese company Pop Mart that started off as a book in a series of books called "The Monsters" writen by Dutch-Hong Kong author, Kasing Lung.
Despite his lack of combat experience, Boneka Ambalabu was a major ally for the crocs in the croco-avian war, supplying them with various weapons, and giving Larili Larila his clock.
history_spanish:
El audio de Boneka Ambalabu no es original; proviene de un video de octubre de 2024. El video original forma parte de una serie sobre Boneka Ambalabu, una muneca con la cara de Dreamybull, un famoso meme de internet.
El nombre "Boneka Ambalabu" proviene de varias palabras, la primera de las cuales es Boneka, que en indonesio significa "muneca". "Ambalabu" es una mezcla de "Ambatukam", una frase frecuente en los memes de Dreamybull que se popularizaron alrededor de 2022, y "Labubu", una muneca de la empresa china Pop Mart que comenzo como un libro de la serie "Los Monstruos", escrita por el autor holandes-hongkones Kasing Lung.
A pesar de su falta de experiencia en combate, Boneka Ambalabu fue un aliado clave de los cocodrilos en la guerra entre cocodrilos y aves, proporcionandoles diversas armas y dandole a Larili Larila su reloj.
inbattle_english: Despite the character's fearsome description, it appears to be rather weak in battle - it doesn't have many ways to attack the opponent. The best abilities he has is sticking out his tongue and rolling in his tire and hitting his opponents with his tire.
inbattle_spanish: A pesar de la temible descripcion del personaje, parece bastante debil en combate: no tiene muchas maneras de atacar al oponente. Sus mejores habilidades son sacar la lengua, rodar en su neumatico y golpear a sus oponentes con el.

name: Brr Brr Patatim
lyrics_italian: Brr, brr, Patapim, il mio cappello e pieno di Slim! Nel bosco fitto e misterioso viveva un essere assai curioso. Con radici intrecciate e gambe incrociate, mani sottili, braccia agitate. Il suo naso lungo come un prosciutto, un po' babbuino, un po' cespugliotto. Si chiamava Patapim, oh che strano, e parlava italiano ma con accento arcano! Un giorno trovo un cappello dorato: "Perfetto!" grido, "che bel risultato!" Ma dentro c'era Slim, il ranocchio blu, che faceva "brr, brr" senza un perche in piu. Patapim piangeva: "Mio caro cappello, ora c'e Slim, che guaio, che duello!" Saltava, rideva, si disperava, ma il ranocchio mai se ne andava. Con foglie sui gomiti e muschio sul mеnto, corse nel bosco spinto dal vento. Ando dal mago Tiramisu chiеdendo aiuto con un gran "ciuu ciuu!" Il mago rispose, mangiando un panino: "Per togliere Slim, serve un palloncino!" Cosi Patapim, con gran confusione, soffio nel pallone con emozione. Slim volo, con un grande "boom", sparendo nel cielo come un bel fungo di fumo! Ora Patapim balla nel vento.
lyrics_english: Brr Brr Patapim, my hat is full of Slim! In the thick and mysterious forest lived a very curious being. With entwined roots and crossed legs, thin hands, waving arms - his nose was long like a ham, a bit baboon, a bit bushy. His name was Patapim, oh, how strange, and he spoke Italian but with an arcane accent! One day, he found a golden hat, “Perfect!” he shouted, “what a great result!” But inside was Slim, the blue frog, who went “Brrr brrr!” without a reason more. Patapim cried: “My dear hat! Now there’s Slim, what a mess, what a spat!” He jumped, laughed, despaired, but the frog never went away. With leaves on his elbows and moss on his chin he ran into the forest pushed by the wind He went to the magician Tiramisu, asking for help with a big “Choo chuhoo!” The magician replied, eating a sandwich: “To remove Slim, you need a balloon!” So Patapim, with great confusion, blew into the balloon with excitement. Slim flew, with a big BOOM, disappearing into the sky like a beautiful mushroom of smoke! Now Patapim dances in the wind.
lyrics_spanish: ¡Brr, brr, Patapim, mi sombrero esta lleno de Slim! En el espeso y misterioso bosque vivia un ser muy curioso. Con raices enredadas y piernas cruzadas, manos delgadas, brazos que se agitaban. Su nariz era larga como un jamon, mitad babuino, mitad peluda. Se llamaba Patapim, ¡oh, que extrano!, y hablaba italiano, ¡pero con un acento arcano! Un dia encontro un sombrero dorado: "¡Perfecto!", exclamo, "¡que bonito resultado!". Pero dentro estaba Slim, la rana azul, que hacia "brr, brr" sin motivo. Patapim grito: "¡Mi querido sombrero, ahora Slim esta aqui, que desastre, que duelo!". Salto, rio, se desespero, pero la rana no se fue. Con hojas en los codos y musgo en la barbilla, corrio hacia el bosque, impulsado por el viento. Fue a ver al mago Tiramisu, pidiendole ayuda con un sonoro "¡chu-chu!". El mago respondio, comiendo un sandwich: "¡Para eliminar a Slim, necesitas un globo!". Patapim, muy confundido, inflo el globo con entusiasmo. Slim volo con un enorme ¡bum!, desapareciendo en el cielo como una hermosa nube de hongo. Ahora Patapim baila en el viento.
personality_english:
The character is mostly known by the name Brr Brr Patapim. However, from his story, it can be seen that his name is actually Patapim, and "Brr Brr" is an onomatopoeia for the sound of the blue frog, Slim.

He is closely related to Tric Trac Barabum, sometimes being called his father.

Despite his peaceful demeanor, he is one of the only known characters to have defeated Tung Tung Tung Sahur in battle.

He has a Brother named Crick Crack Gulp

In the story of Brr Brr I'm a Car, he was known for having smelly feet. The creator added it in to the story because of a funny video about him having smelly feet.
personality_spanish:
El personaje es conocido principalmente por el nombre Brr Brr Patapim. Sin embargo, de su historia se desprende que su nombre es Patapim, y "Brr Brr" es una onomatopeya del sonido de la rana azul, Slim.

Es pariente cercano de Tric Trac Barabum, y a veces se le llama su padre.

A pesar de su caracter pacifico, es uno de los pocos personajes conocidos que ha derrotado a Tung Tung Tung Sahur en batalla.

Tiene un hermano llamado Crick Crack Gulp.

En la historia de Brr Brr I'm a Car, era conocido por tener mal olor de pies. El creador lo anadio a la historia debido a un video gracioso sobre el con mal olor de pies.
history_english:
Brr Brr Patapim is an Italian Brainrot created by TikTok user @ofuscabreno on the 18th of February, 2025. 

It is depicted as a hybrid creature, combining features of a giant proboscis monkey and a tree. Brr Brr Patapim has notably large feet, with legs intertwined with tree branches, while its small hands emerge from its head. Its body is predominantly covered in leaves, except for its feet. In visual representations, Brr Brr Patapim is often shown standing on a cement road within a forested background. He hates the blue frog Slim.
history_spanish:
Brr Brr Patapim es un Brainrot italiano creado por el usuario de TikTok @ofuscabreno el 18 de febrero de 2025.

Se le representa como una criatura hibrida que combina caracteristicas de un mono narigudo gigante y un arbol. Brr Brr Patapim tiene pies notablemente grandes, con las piernas entrelazadas con las ramas de los arboles, mientras que sus pequenas manos emergen de su cabeza. Su cuerpo esta cubierto predominantemente de hojas, excepto sus pies. En representaciones visuales, Brr Brr Patapim suele aparecer de pie en un camino de cemento con un fondo boscoso. Odia a la rana azul Slim.
reception_english: Brr Brr Patapim initially wasn't very popular, but after some time he became one of the most beloved characters in the fandom. Viewers were endeared by his wholesome, yet menacing appearence and his beautiful, heart-wrenching story. He also inspired fans to create similar characters, such as Tric Trac Barabum, Patapimus Maximus, Brr Brr Tarflem, Brr Brr Mamabim and Crick Crack Gulp
reception_spanish: Brr Brr Patapim no fue muy popular al principio, pero con el tiempo se convirtio en uno de los personajes mas queridos del fandom. Los espectadores se enamoraron de su apariencia sana y a la vez amenazante, y de su hermosa y conmovedora historia. Tambien inspiro a los fans a crear personajes similares, como Tric Trac Barabum, Patapimus Maximus, Brr Brr Tarflem, Brr Brr Mamabim y Crick Crack Gulp.
inbattle_english: The character is generally seen as a benevolent creature, and in battles, isn't depicted as a very strong fighter, despite his size. His lack of proper arms is limiting his potential in battle, which makes him lose most matchups. He usually uses powers such as transformation, but this does not always work in his favor. His most famous fight was against Tung Tung Tung Sahur, which he won by crushing Tung Tung Tung Sahur with his giant feet. So he’s still pretty strong for the small brainrots because he can crush them with his giant feet so As part tree, Brr Brr Patapim can root into the ground, control moss and vines, and even cause rapid forest growth to entangle enemies or escape if he needs to.
inbattle_spanish: El personaje es generalmente visto como una criatura benevola, y en batallas, no es representado como un luchador muy fuerte, a pesar de su tamano. Su falta de brazos adecuados esta limitando su potencial en la batalla, lo que le hace perder la mayoria de los enfrentamientos. Suele usar poderes como la transformacion, pero esto no siempre funciona a su favor. Su pelea mas famosa fue contra Tung Tung Tung Sahur, que gano aplastando a Tung Tung Tung Sahur con sus pies gigantes. Asi que sigue siendo bastante fuerte para los pequenos brainrots porque puede aplastarlos con sus pies gigantes. Como parte arbol, Brr Brr Patapim puede enraizar en el suelo, controlar el musgo y las enredaderas, e incluso provocar un rapido crecimiento del bosque para enredar a los enemigos o escapar si es necesario.

name: Cacto hipopotamo
lyrics_italian: cacto-ipopotamo. C’era una volta un cactus gigante con una testa di ipopotamo elegante. Nel deserto, tanto caldo e vasto, due sandali giganti come un casto. Il cactus camminava sotto il sole splendente, con le sandali sorprendenti e lucenti. Per tutto il deserto, dove la sabbia si muove, camminava solo mentre il vento scuote. L’ipopotamo rispondeva cosi, con ogni passo. «Vieni qui!» Il vento soffiava, forte e feroce, ma il cactus non fermava, seguiva la sua voce. Cammino e cammino, senza mai fermarsi, in un mondo vasto, dove il sole non si puo abbracciare. Con le sandali e la testa forte, aspettava il destino, oltre la morte. Deserto infinito, senza fine, senza amore, il cactus e le sandali temevano il dolore. Quando il sole cala, il freddo arrivera e con un sorriso il cactus riposera.
lyrics_english: cacto-ipopotamo. Once upon a time there was a giant cactus with an elegant hippopotamus head. In the desert, so hot and vast, two giant sandals like a chaste tree. The cactus walked under the bright sun, with the surprising and shiny sandals. Throughout the desert, where the sand moves, he walked only when the wind shakes. The hippopotamus responded like this, with every step. "Come here!" The wind blew, strong and fierce, but the cactus did not stop, he followed its voice. He walked and walked, never stopping, in a vast world, where the sun cannot be embraced. With the sandals and the strong head, he awaited destiny, beyond death. Infinite desert, without end, without love, the cactus and the sandals feared the pain. When the sun goes down, the cold will come and with a smile the cactus will rest.
lyrics_spanish: Cactus-hipopotamo. Erase una vez un cactus gigante con una elegante cabeza de hipopotamo. En el desierto, tan caluroso y vasto, dos sandalias gigantes como un arbol casto. El cactus caminaba bajo el sol brillante, con las sorprendentes y brillantes sandalias. Por el desierto, donde la arena se mueve, caminaba solo cuando el viento la agitaba. El hipopotamo respondia asi, a cada paso: "¡Ven aqui!". El viento soplaba, fuerte y feroz, pero el cactus no se detenia, seguia su voz. Camino y camino, sin detenerse, en un mundo vasto, donde el sol no se puede abrazar. Con las sandalias y la cabeza fuerte, esperaba el destino, mas alla de la muerte. Desierto infinito, sin fin, sin amor, el cactus y las sandalias temian al dolor. Cuando el sol se ponga, llegara el frio y, con una sonrisa, el cactus descansara.

history_english: “Lirili / Larila” – The name is built in a nonsense rhyme style common in Italian Brainrot characters (similar to Tralalero Tralala). It mimics the rhythm of Italian children’s songs and carnival chants. The repetition and vowel-heavy sounds (-li / -la) give it a playful, surreal quality. Possible Italian roots: “Lira” (old Italian currency or musical instrument) → hinting at rhythm/music. “Li” (there) & “La” (there) → literally means “here and there,” which matches his wandering desert lore. Cultural Playfulness: His name is intentionally whimsical, evoking a nursery rhyme or circus chant. Just like his character, the name suggests randomness, movement, and surreal comedy.
history_spanish: “Lirili / Larila” – El nombre esta construido en un estilo de rima sin sentido comun en los personajes italianos de Brainrot (similar a Tralalero Tralala). Imita el ritmo de las canciones infantiles italianas y los cantos de carnaval. La repeticion y los sonidos vocalicos (-li / -la) le dan una cualidad ludica y surrealista. Posibles raices italianas: “Lira” (antigua moneda italiana o instrumento musical) → insinuando ritmo/musica. “Li” (alli) y “La” (alli) → significan literalmente “aqui y alla”, lo que coincide con su tradicion errante del desierto. Alegria cultural: Su nombre es intencionalmente caprichoso, evocando una cancion infantil o un canto de circo. Al igual que su personaje, el nombre sugiere aleatoriedad, movimiento y comedia surrealista.
reception_english: Its absurd, repetitive style makes it catchy and entertaining, often used in memes, edits, and remixes. Many find it funny because of its ridiculous name and chaotic vibe, turning it into a sort of inside joke among fans. Still, it’s divisive: while some see it as a fun example of absurd humor, others think it’s annoying or overly repetitive. Even so, although it isn’t as big as other figures like Tralalelo or Kurkur, Lirili Larila remains recognizable and appreciated as a minor yet persistent icon of the trend.
reception_spanish: Su estilo repetitivo y absurdo la convirtio en un personaje pegajoso y divertido, muy utilizado en memes, remixes y ediciones de video. Para muchos usuarios, es graciosa precisamente por lo ridiculo de su nombre y el tono caotico que transmite, lo que la ha hecho un “codigo interno” dentro de la comunidad. Sin embargo, tambien es polarizante: mientras unos la ven como un icono divertido del humor absurdo, otros la consideran molesta o demasiado repetitiva. Aun asi, aunque no tiene tanta fuerza como personajes mas grandes como Tralalelo o Kurkur, Lirili Larila sigue siendo reconocible y valorada como un simbolo menor pero constante dentro del fenomeno.
inbattle_english: He is often cited to have the ability to control time through the alarm clock. This makes him have a powerful performance in battle, even defeating Tung Tung Tung Sahur and Tralalero Tralala. He has also been able to defeat characters like Cappuccino Assassino by just stomping him with his giant feet/sandals.
inbattle_spanish: A menudo se le atribuye la capacidad de controlar el tiempo mediante el despertador. Esto le otorga un desempeno impresionante en combate, incluso derrotando a Tung Tung Tung Sahur y Tralalero Tralala. Tambien ha podido derrotar a personajes como Cappuccino Assassino simplemente pisoteandolo con sus gigantescas sandalias.

Rapidamente obtuvo el estatus de criatura favorita de los fans, siendo colocado con frecuencia en los primeros lugares de las clasificaciones creadas por los usuarios. Sin embargo, tambien ha generado controversia por su narracion. Los espectadores han considerado frases como "Non crede in Allah" y "bombarda i bambini a Gaza e in Palestina" ofensivas y una burla al conflicto militar en Gaza.
inbattle_english: In battle, Bombardiro Crocodilo is often considered one of the strongest characters in the universe due to his sheer physical power. inbattle_spanish: En batalla, Bombardiro Crocodilo suele ser considerado uno de los personajes mas fuertes del universo debido a su enorme poder fisico. Su cuerpo, al ser el de un avion bombardero, es suficiente para superar facilmente a la mayoria de los personajes. Su tecnica principal consiste en perseguir a su oponente y dejar caer una bomba sobre el desde el cielo.

inbattle_english:
Pre-upgrade
He is weaker than his brother, Bombardiro Crocodilo, due to his limited weaponry. Despite this, he has potential to be strong, but doesn't have enough resources to be.

Post-upgrade
He is a lot stronger, but still not one of the strongest even with his newfound powers, because he can revert to a weaker state when Lirili Larila dies.

Weapons + Abilities
Grenade Launchers: Can fire up to 50 feet ahead but then drops to the ground. Only viable for point blank or bombing

Large grenades: 10 500lb grenades on the sides are viable for carpet bombing.

Life-Link: Bombomini Gusini can be upgraded to be more powerful, but relies on the person who upgraded him to be alive in order to keep it.

missiles: he has missiles he can shoot. When in battle he can continuously fire missiles at his opponent.

Superpowers
He has infinite ammo and can produce atomic bombs out of the blue. He has the ability to teleport to anywhere. However, prior to his upgrade by the hands of Lirili Larila (during the Croco-Avian wars), his arsenal is weaker than his brothers's.
inbattle_spanish:
Antes de la mejora  
Es mas debil que su hermano, Bombardiro Crocodilo, debido a su armamento limitado. A pesar de esto, tiene potencial para ser fuerte, pero no cuenta con los recursos suficientes para lograrlo.

Despues de la mejora  
Es mucho mas fuerte, aunque sigue sin ser uno de los mas poderosos incluso con sus nuevos poderes, ya que puede volver a un estado mas debil cuando Lirili Larila muere.

Armas y habilidades  
- Lanzagranadas: Puede disparar hasta 15 metros hacia adelante antes de que el proyectil caiga al suelo. Solo es util a corta distancia o para bombardeos.  
- Granadas grandes: Posee 10 granadas de 500 libras en los costados, utiles para bombardeos en alfombra.  
- Vinculo vital: Bombombini Gusini puede ser mejorado para volverse mas poderoso, pero depende de que la persona que lo mejoro siga viva para mantener ese poder.  
- Misiles: Tiene misiles que puede disparar. En combate puede lanzarlos continuamente contra su oponente.  

Superpoderes  
Tiene municion infinita y puede producir bombas atomicas de la nada. Tambien posee la capacidad de teletransportarse a cualquier lugar. Sin embargo, antes de su mejora por las manos de Lirili Larila (durante las guerras Croco-Aviares), su arsenal era mas debil que el de su hermano.

name: Cavallo Virtuoso
lyrics_italian: Ecco Cavallo Virtuoso, Uno Show Strepitoso. Era una volta un cavallo stravagante. Testa di equino, corpo brillante. Non di muscoli, ne di velluto, Ma di legno e corde, un suono assoluto. Con stivali neri, grandi e lucenti, Suonava il piano tra mille genti. Bailava il tango, suonava il jazz, Un vero prodigio, un artista da paz! "Buongiorno, amigos! Lo sono Juan. Suono, ballo e mangio flan!" Diceva ridendo, girando in pista, Con pose da star, un vero artista. Un giorno a Milano, nel centro affollato, Scivolo sul pavimento bagnato. "Mamma mia! Che cosa e successo?". Cadde di schiena, ma rise lo stesso. Il pubblico rise, poi lo applaudi. E lui con un salto di nuovo parti. "Non ho paura, io sono speciale! Un cavallo pianista? Idea geniale!" Arrivo un gatto chiamato Pierrot, Faceva il balletto, un piccolo show. Juan sorrise: "Dai, balla con me!". E il duo danzava con grande cachet. Su spiagge dorate e piazze giganti, Ovunque brillava tra mille diamanti. E nei cuori di tutti resto il suo sorriso, Cavallo Virtuoso, un suono preciso!
lyrics_english: Ecco Cavallo Virtuoso, A Spectacular Show. Once upon a time, there was a quirky horse. A horse's head, a dazzling body. Not of muscles, nor of velvet, But of wood and strings, an absolute sound. With black boots, big and shiny, He played the piano among thousands of people. He danced the tango, he played jazz, A true prodigy, a crazy good artist! "Good morning, friends! I am Juan. I play, I dance, and I eat flan!" He said laughing, spinning on the floor, With star-like poses, a true performer. One day in Milan, in the crowded center, He slipped on the wet pavement. "Mamma mia! What just happened?" He fell on his back, but still laughed. The audience laughed, then applauded him. And with a jump, he was off again. "I'm not afraid, I'm something unique! A pianist horse? What a genius idea!" Along came a cat named Pierrot, Who danced ballet, a little show. Juan smiled: "Come on, dance with me!" And the duo danced with great prestige. On golden beaches and giant squares, They shone everywhere like a thousand diamonds. And in everyone's hearts remained his smile, Virtuoso Horse, a flawless sound!

No de musculos ni de terciopelo, sino de madera y cuerdas, un sonido absoluto. Con botas negras, grandes y relucientes, tocaba el piano entre miles de personas. Bailaba tango, tocaba jazz, ¡un verdadero prodigio, un artista total!  
“¡Buenos dias, amigos! Soy Juan. ¡Toco, bailo y como flan!” —decia riendo mientras giraba en la pista, con poses de estrella, un verdadero artista.  
Un dia en Milan, en el centro lleno de gente, resbalo en el suelo mojado. “¡Mamma mia! ¿Que ha pasado?” Cayo de espaldas, pero aun asi se rio. El publico se rio tambien y luego lo aplaudio. Y con un salto, volvio a empezar.  
“No tengo miedo, ¡soy especial! ¿Un caballo pianista? ¡Que idea genial!”  
Entonces llego un gato llamado Pierrot, que hacia ballet, un pequeno espectaculo. Juan sonrio: “¡Vamos, baila conmigo!”. Y el duo bailo con gran estilo. En playas doradas y plazas gigantes, brillaban por todas partes como mil diamantes. Y en el corazon de todos quedo su sonrisa: Cavallo Virtuoso, ¡un sonido perfecto!

name: Frigo Camelo
lyrics_italian: Frigo Camello Buffo Fardello. Nel centro della citta, tra macchine e calore, un frigo camelo cammina con amore. Con stivali giganti e passo lento, ha perso la gioia, ha perso il momento. Che freddo qui dentro, dice senza sorriso. Ma nel deserto non c'e piu paradiso. Latte e burro, ora disorganizzato, continua da solo, sempre piu stanco. Per Roma, Parigi, Madrid e Milano, tutti dicono che tristezza, che disperazione. Sotto il sole, caldo e ardente, il frigo si scioglie e lui continua triste, sofferente. Frigo camelo, sommerso e perduto, con il suo carico, va verso un destino sofferto. Da Lisbona a Firenze, senza piu speranza, la sua strada e lunga, senza alcuna ricompensa. E ora a Londra, tutto e piu pesante, con occhi stanchi, gia senza essere notati.
lyrics_english: Frigo Camello, funny burden. In the heart of the city, between cars and heat a fridge camel walks with love. With giant boots and a slow step, he has lost joy, he has lost the moment. "It's cold in here," he says without a smile. "But in the desert, there is no more paradise. Milk and butter now disorganized." He continues alone, more tired, through Rome, Paris, Madrid and Milan. Everyone says, "What sadness, what despair." Under the hot and burning sun the fridge melts and he keeps going, sad and suffering. Frigo Camello, submerged and lost with his load, heads toward a suffering fate from Lisbon to Florence without hope. His long journey without any reward, and now in London everything is heavier, with tired eyes, already unnoticed.
lyrics_spanish:
Frigo Camelo, carga divertida. En el corazon de la ciudad, entre autos y calor, un camello nevera camina con amor.  
Con botas gigantes y paso lento, ha perdido la alegria, ha perdido el momento.  
“Hace frio aqui dentro”, dice sin sonrisa. “Pero en el desierto ya no hay paraiso.  
La leche y la mantequilla ahora estan desordenadas”.  
Continua solo, cada vez mas cansado, por Roma, Paris, Madrid y Milan.  
Todos dicen: “Que tristeza, que desesperacion”.  
Bajo el sol caliente y ardiente, la nevera se derrite y el sigue, triste y sufriente.  
Frigo Camelo, sumergido y perdido, con su carga va hacia un destino doloroso.  
De Lisboa a Florencia, sin esperanza, su camino es largo y sin recompensa.  
Y ahora en Londres, todo es mas pesado, con ojos cansados, ya sin ser notado.

history_english: On February 9th, 2025, TikToker @ofuscabreno shared a meme featuring an AI-generated image of a camel with a fridge body and Timberland boots. The video quickly went viral, amassing over 2.5 million views in just two months. The video includes a text-to-speech narration that humorously addresses the oddity of the hybrid creature.
history_spanish:
El 9 de febrero de 2025, el tiktoker @ofuscabreno compartio un meme que mostraba una imagen generada por IA de un camello con cuerpo de nevera y botas Timberland.  
El video se volvio viral rapidamente, acumulando mas de 2.5 millones de vistas en solo dos meses.  
El video incluye una narracion de texto a voz que comenta con humor lo extrano de esta criatura hibrida.
reception_english:
The meme became increasingly popularized over the following weeks alongside other examples of AI brainrot animals, including by brands.

For example, on February 24th, 2025, the @samsungnederland TikTok page posted a meme featuring a Samsung-brand Frigo Camelo, gathering over 2 million views in just over a month.
reception_spanish:
El meme se popularizo cada vez mas en las semanas siguientes, junto a otros ejemplos de animales de brainrot generados por IA, incluso por parte de marcas.  

Por ejemplo, el 24 de febrero de 2025, la cuenta de TikTok @samsungnederland publico un meme con una version de Frigo Camelo de marca Samsung, alcanzando mas de 2 millones de vistas en poco mas de un mes.
inbattle_english: While useless in direct 1v1 battles, Frigo Camelo is a valuable asset in group battles, able to store and replenish energy for his group, leading to a superior overall stamina. He is also fairly effective at evading attacks due to his relatively fast movement speed. If Frigo Camelo is fighting in hot environments he has a severe disadvantage due to his melting refrigerator body.
inbattle_spanish:
Aunque es inutil en combates directos uno a uno, Frigo Camelo es un recurso valioso en batallas grupales,  
capaz de almacenar y reponer energia para su equipo, lo que les da una resistencia superior.  
Tambien es bastante eficaz para esquivar ataques debido a su velocidad de movimiento relativamente alta.  
Sin embargo, si Frigo Camelo lucha en ambientes calurosos, tiene una gran desventaja debido a su cuerpo de nevera que se derrite.

Konon katanya kalau ada orang yang dipanggil sahur tiga kali dan tidak nyaut, maka makhluk ini datang di rumah kalian. Hiiii, seramnya! Tung tung ini biasanya bersuara layaknya pukulan kentungan sepereti ini. Tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung! Share ke teman kalian yang susah sahur.

It is said that if someone is called for sahur three times and does not answer, then this creature will come to your house. Ahhh, how scary! This Tung tung usually makes a sound like a gong like this. Tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung! Share this with your friends who have trouble eating sahur.
lyrics_spanish: Tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung Sahur. Una aterradora anomalia que aparece durante el Sahur. Se dice que si alguien es llamado para el sahur tres veces y no responde, esta criatura vendra a tu casa. ¡Ahhh, que miedo! Este Tung tung normalmente hace un sonido como un gong, asi: Tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung, tung. Compartelo con tus amigos que tienen problemas para levantarse a comer en el sahur.
personality_english:
Tung Tung Tung Sahur is an anthropomorphic wooden drum who wields a baseball bat as a weapon

According to the sound, if you are called for "Sahur" and do not respond/eat Sahur, then "Tung Tung Tung Sahur" will come for you.

In "Tung Tung Tung", the "Tungs" are onomatopoeic; they represent the beat of the Kentongan before "Sahur". Sahur is a tradition in many Islamic countries where Muslims have food at dawn before the sun rises on the first day of Ramadan, before the fasting of Ramadan.
personality_spanish:
Tung Tung Tung Sahur es un tambor de madera antropomorfico que empuna un bate de beisbol como arma.

Segun la leyenda, si te llaman para el “Sahur” y no respondes ni comes, “Tung Tung Tung Sahur” vendra por ti.

En “Tung Tung Tung”, los “Tungs” son onomatopeyicos; representan los golpes del *Kentongan* antes del Sahur. El Sahur es una tradicion en muchos paises islamicos donde los musulmanes comen antes del amanecer en el primer dia del Ramadan, antes de comenzar el ayuno.
history_english: Tung Tung Tung Sahur (properly Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Sahur) is an Indonesian Brainrot character published on the 28th of February, 2025.
history_spanish: Tung Tung Tung Sahur (formalmente Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Sahur) es un personaje de Brainrot indonesio publicado el 28 de febrero de 2025.
reception_english:
Tung Tung Tung Sahur quickly became the most popular creature in the Italian/Indoniesan Brainrot universe. It had a huge impact on the community - it popularized the usage of the "Песня для твоего друга" sound (also known as "The Sound Of Your Fear"), with the song becoming the most commonly used background music for Italian Brainrot. It also led to the creation of many similar characters, such as Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Sahur.

Among the Italian Brainrot community, Tung Tung Tung Sahur is one of the most popular characters In Italian brainrot History, often taking the top spot in rankings and being considered the main character alongside Tralalero Tralala and Bombardiro Crocodilo.
reception_spanish:
Tung Tung Tung Sahur se convirtio rapidamente en la criatura mas popular del universo Italian/Indonesian Brainrot. Tuvo un gran impacto en la comunidad: popularizo el uso del sonido "Песня для твоего друга" (tambien conocido como “El sonido de tu miedo”), que se volvio la musica de fondo mas utilizada en los videos de Brainrot italiano. 

Tambien inspiro la creacion de muchos personajes similares, como Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Ta Sahur.

Dentro de la comunidad de Italian Brainrot, Tung Tung Tung Sahur es uno de los personajes mas populares en toda la historia, ocupando a menudo los primeros lugares en los rankings y siendo considerado un personaje principal junto a Tralalero Tralala y Bombardiro Crocodilo.
inbattle_english: The character is often cited as the strongest character in the entire universe. This aura comes from the powerful bat it weilds and its supernatural abilities (appearing as a scary anomaly). Along with simply hitting its opponents with its weapon, it is also famously known for being able to transform into a more powerful form - a giant wooden gorilla. Thanks to this transformation ability, it is very hard for opponents to win against Tung Tung Tung Sahur.
inbattle_spanish:
El personaje es considerado con frecuencia como el mas poderoso de todo el universo. Su fuerza proviene del bate que empuna y de sus habilidades sobrenaturales (aparece como una aterradora anomalia). 

Ademas de golpear a sus oponentes con su arma, es conocido por poder transformarse en una forma mas poderosa: un gorila de madera gigante. Gracias a esta habilidad de transformacion, es muy dificil que sus enemigos puedan vencer a Tung Tung Tung Sahur.

No one can stop him in dog racing, because this dog uses his watermelon aura and turbo fuel to destroy the road. The forest is his passion, and he enjoys climbing trees and eating sunflower seeds. But this dog wasn't like this before. Several years ago, a Bulgarian scientist discovered the formula for combining a watermelon with his brown dog. He poured cyanide on the watermelon and injected the dog with the anesthetic. Then the scientist combined them in his car, and this was the result.

Hace varios anos, un cientifico bulgaro descubrio la formula para combinar una sandia con su perro marron. Vertio cianuro sobre la sandia e inyecto anestesia en el perro. Luego, el cientifico los combino en su maquina, y este fue el resultado.

name: Se Se Se Serio Sahur
lyrics_italian:
Serio, serio, sahur!
Se se se serio sahur!
Faccia di marmo, cuore di pietra,
nessun sorriso, pura etichetta.

"Legga cento anni di serieta!" 📖
dice il cervo, dice papa!
Pongasi serio, ciervo 🗣
non ridere mai, e troppo tardi, fratello!

Serio come muro, fermo come sasso,
Se se se sahur, non fa un passo falso.
"Silenzio! Niente risate!" dice lui,
con gli occhi grandi e l’anima blu.

Se se se serio sahur!
Il mattone del rispetto, del rigor!
Con la fronte dritta, con l’onor,
porta la serieta nel cuor!
lyrics_english:
Serious, serious, sahur!
Se se se serious sahur!
Stone face, iron mind,
no smile — discipline time!

“Read a hundred years of seriousness!” 📖
says the deer, no less!
Get serious, deer 🗣!
No jokes here, crystal clear!

Serious like wall, solid like rock,
Se se se sahur, always on clock.
“Silence! No laughs!” he declares,
with wide eyes and steady stares.

Se se se serious sahur!
The brick of respect, the core!
With a steady look, pure decor,
he brings the seriousness forevermore!
lyrics_spanish:
Serio, serio, sahur!
Se se se serio sahur!
Cara de piedra, mente de acero,
ni una sonrisa, todo sincero.

“Lease cien anos de seriedad” 📖
grita el ciervo con autoridad.
¡Pongase serio, ciervo 🗣!
Nada de risas, que esto es en serio.

Serio como muro, firme como bloque,
Se se se sahur, nunca se equivoque.
“Silencio total, no hay humor”,
dice mirando con puro rigor.

Se se se serio sahur!
El ladrillo del respeto y el honor!
Con mirada fija, sin temblor,
lleva la seriedad en su corazon!
personality_english: 100% serious, he truly knows how to handle seriousness and tries to make others handle it too.

lyrics_italian: Cocofanto Elefanto Elefantucci Coconucci! Questo bambino e protetto da una noce di cocco. Insieme non hanno paura di nessuna avversita. Viaggiano nella giungla in cerca di avventure.
lyrics_english: Cocofanto Elephanto, Elefantucci Coconucci! This child is protected by a coconut. Together they are not afraid of any adversity. They travel in the jungle in search of adventures.
lyrics_spanish: ¡Cocofanto Elefanto, Elefantucci Coconucci! Este nino esta protegido por un coco. Juntos no temen ninguna adversidad. Viajan por la selva en busca de aventuras.
personality_english: Cocofanto Elefanto is a playful fusion of a baby elephant and a coconut. His round, coconut-shaped body keeps him small, limiting his growth, but adds to his charm. He often wears a wide, cheerful smile and sometimes dribbles coconut milk or water. He lives in the dense jungle, where his stubby legs and rounded ears make him look both clumsy and adorable. Despite his size, he’s curious and adventurous, exploring his surroundings with bright, lively eyes. His coconut body also acts as natural protection, keeping him safe while he roams his leafy playground. Cocofanto is a magical, cheerful creature, blending tropical whimsy with elephantine cuteness, instantly memorable to anyone who encounters him.
personality_spanish: Cocofanto Elefanto es una fusion juguetona entre un elefante bebe y un coco. Su cuerpo redondo con forma de coco lo mantiene pequeno, limitando su crecimiento, pero aumentando su encanto. Suele llevar una amplia sonrisa alegre y, a veces, deja caer leche o agua de coco. Vive en la densa jungla, donde sus patas cortas y orejas redondeadas lo hacen ver torpe y adorable a la vez. A pesar de su tamano, es curioso y aventurero, explorando su entorno con ojos brillantes y llenos de vida. Su cuerpo de coco tambien actua como una proteccion natural, manteniendolo a salvo mientras recorre su entorno selvatico. Cocofanto es una criatura magica y alegre que mezcla el encanto tropical con la ternura de un elefante, siendo inolvidable para quien lo ve.
history_english: Cocofanto Elefanto is an Italian Brainrot character by @alexey_pigeon. Cocofanto elefanto is a combination of a baby elephant and a coconut. He is smiling and is standing in the dense jungle. He is also very adorable!
history_spanish: Cocofanto Elefanto es un personaje del Italian Brainrot creado por @alexey_pigeon. Es una combinacion entre un elefante bebe y un coco. Siempre sonrie y se encuentra de pie en la densa jungla. ¡Ademas, es muy adorable!

name: Giraffa Celeste
lyrics_italian: Giraffa Celeste, viaggio agreste. Dans la lune tutta dorata, la giraffa saltava molto incantata. Con scarponi e casco brillante, nel vuoto danzava leggera e vibrante. Ma tra les etoile un'ombra appari Anelli giganti brillava li Che strano pianeta, che viso bovino. Forse un miraggio, un sogno divino. L'ombra si gira, occhi di fuoco, soy saturnita no juego poco. Camino forte soy legendaria, tra le galassie storia contraria Giraffa sospira poi fa un passo. Sente un destino, non un collasso, danzano insieme, senza paura. Tra luce e spazio, dolce avventura, e mentre il tempo piano svanisce Il loro incontro mai piu finisce. Un'anima strana, un corpo celeste, leggende unite, nessuno riveste. Sotto il cielo brillante e infinito, si fondono insieme, il viaggio e finito. Tra stelle danzanti e sogni senza fine, si scrive una leggenda che mai svanisce, sublime.
lyrics_english: Celestial Giraffe, a rustic journey. In the golden moon above, the giraffe leapt, enchanted with love. With boots and a helmet shining bright, he danced through the void, glowing with light, But among the stars, a shadow drew near Giant rings glittered, distant yet clear What a strange planet, with a bovine face, perhaps a mirage, or a divine embrace. The shadow turned, eyes like fire, "Im Saturnita, i don't play small. I walk strong, I am legendary, through galaxies, my tale is contrary." The giraffe sighed, then took a step near. She felt her fate, no trace of fear. They danced together, bold and free, through light and space, a sweet odyssey. And as time slowly faded away, their meeting would forever stay. A strange soul, a body celestial, two legends merged, nothing superficial. Beneath the brilliant, endless sky, they fused as one, no need to ask why. Among dancing stars and dreams that don't cease, a legend is written, eternal in peace, Sublime.
lyrics_spanish: Jirafa Celeste, viaje agreste. En la luna dorada, la jirafa saltaba encantada. Con botas y casco brillante, danzaba en el vacio, ligera y vibrante. Pero entre las estrellas aparecio una sombra, con anillos gigantes que brillaban a la distancia. Que planeta tan extrano, con rostro bovino. Tal vez un espejismo, o un sueno divino. La sombra se giro, con ojos de fuego: “Soy Saturnita, no juego poco. Camino fuerte, soy legendaria, entre galaxias mi historia contraria.” La jirafa suspira y da un paso. Siente su destino, no un colapso. Bailan juntas, sin temor, entre luz y espacio, dulce esplendor. Y mientras el tiempo lentamente se desvanece, su encuentro eterno permanece. Un alma extrana, un cuerpo celeste, leyendas unidas, nada que las veste. Bajo el cielo brillante e infinito, se funden en uno, el viaje ha concluido. Entre estrellas danzantes y suenos sin fin, se escribe una leyenda que nunca tendra fin. Sublime.

His story/lyrics are one of the most majestic in the Italian Brainrot universe, similar to that of Brr Brr Patapim. Video by TikTok user @ofuscabreno, he plans to go to Chickino Jupiterino soon and study her egg moons and intense radiation
personality_spanish: Giraffa Celeste es aliada de La Vacca Saturno Saturnita, Dragonino Alginoves y otros amigos. Esta relacionada con Ganganzelli Trulala, siendo primos. Su historia y letra son de las mas majestuosas del universo Italian Brainrot, similar a la de Brr Brr Patapim. name: La Vaca Saturnita
lyrics_italian:
La Vacca Saturno Saturnita.
Defrente [sic] tu sei tanto bonita [sic],
con il corpo di Saturno, Saturnita.
Gli anelli che girano, brillano al cielo,
una vacca spaziale senza alcun velo.
Con due piedi giganti cammina sul marciapiede.
Le persone la guardano, si fermano, si credono un po' sordi,
i bambini gridano: "Ma che cosa e [sic] questa?".
Saturnita sorride, come se fosse una festa.
"Che cosa e questa vacca? Un sogno o realta?",
chiedono gli adulti, senza alcuna verita.
Saturnita cammina tranquilla e felice,
portando risate come una luce.
"Voglio solo ballare senza paura",
pensava Saturnita, con gioia e bravura.
Ogni passo che fa, i piedi fanno rumore,
e tutti ridono pieni di amore.
Alla fine della giornata, quando il sole si spegne,
Saturnita sorride, pronta a tornare.
Domani sara un altro giorno brillante,
portando risate e un futuro gigante.
lyrics_english: La Vacca Saturno Saturnita. From the front [sic] you are so beautiful [sic], with the body of Saturn, Saturnita. The rotating rings shine in the sky, an unveiled space cow. With two giant feet she walks along the sidewalk. People look at her, stop, think she is a little deaf, children shout: "But what is this?" Saturnita smiles, as if it were a celebration. "What is this cow? A dream or reality?" the adults ask, without any truth. Saturnita walks calmly and happily, bringing laughter like a light. "I just want to dance without fear," thought Saturnita, with joy and skill. With each step she takes, her feet make noise, and everyone laughs full of love. At the end of the day, when the sun sets, Saturnita smiles, ready to return. Tomorrow will be another bright day, bringing laughter and a giant future. The Saturn Cow Saturnita. From the front [sic] you are so beautiful [sic], with the body of Saturn, Saturnita. Spinning rings glitter in the sky, an unveiled space cow. With two giant feet, she walks down the sidewalk. People stare, stop, and think she's a little deaf. Children shout, "What's this?" Saturnita smiles, as if celebrating. "What is this cow? A dream or reality?" the adults ask, without any truth. Saturnita walks calmly and happily, bringing laughter like a light. "I just want to dance without fear," thought Saturnita, with joy and skill. With every step she takes, her feet make a sound, and everyone laughs, full of love. At the end of the day, as the sun sets, Saturnita smiles, ready to return. Tomorrow will be another bright day, bringing laughter and a giant future.
lyrics_spanish: La Vacca Saturno Saturnita. Defrente [sic] eres tan hermosa [sic], con el cuerpo de Saturno, Saturnita. Los anillos giratorios brillan en el cielo, una vaca espacial sin velo. Con dos pies gigantes camina por la acera. La gente la mira, se detiene, piensa que esta un poco sorda, los ninos gritan: "¿Pero que es esto?" Saturnita sonrie, como si fuera una celebracion. "¿Que es esta vaca? ¿Un sueno o realidad?" preguntan los adultos, sin ninguna verdad. Saturnita camina tranquila y feliz, trayendo risas como una luz. "Solo quiero bailar sin miedo", penso Saturnita, con alegria y destreza. Con cada paso que da, sus pies hacen ruido, y todos rien llenos de amor. Al final del dia, cuando el sol se pone, Saturnita sonrie, lista para regresar. Manana sera otro dia brillante, trayendo risas y un futuro gigante.
personality_english:
Similar to Brr Brr Patapim, she has a fairy-tale-like quality, smiling at people and young children while spreading happiness. Her character is healthier and easier to understand than those relying on bizarre explanations or profanity.

Like the character Lirili Larila, La Vacca Saturno Saturnita's presence in videos is often downplayed to avoid conflict. However, she is actually the strongest character, possessing universal-scale abilities akin to a black hole

personality_english:
Nuclearo Dinossauro is a fictional, heavily militarized, cybernetic dinosaur depicted as a flying, nuclear-capable creature. It is often portrayed in speculative media as a hybrid between a mechanized theropod dinosaur and a strategic bomber aircraft, combining features of prehistoric fauna, advanced robotics, and modern aerial warfare.

Nuclearo Dinossauro possesses a large, reptilian frame with extensive metallic augmentations, including wings capable of sustained flight andmor plating designed to withstand high-altitude combat. It typically features an aerodynamic, dragon-like design and is shown carrying or integrating modern missile systems. A distinguishing trait is its fusion-powered thrusters and integrated bomb payloads, suggesting strategic nuclear capabilities.

In the image above, Nuclearo Dinossauro is depicted mid-air, attacking or intercepting Bombardiro Crocodilo—suggesting superiority over its enemy. Its expression and posture imply intelligence and tactical awareness, but despite his immense power, he is still outclassed by way stronger bombers such as Nuclearo Mosassauro, or Nuclearo Plesiossauro.
personality_spanish:
Nuclearo Dinossauro es un dinosaurio cibernetico ficticio, fuertemente militarizado, representado como una criatura voladora con capacidad nuclear. A menudo se lo representa en medios especulativos como un hibrido entre un dinosaurio teropodo mecanizado y un bombardero estrategico, combinando caracteristicas de la fauna prehistorica, la robotica avanzada y la guerra aerea moderna. 

El Nuclearo Dinossauro posee una gran estructura de reptil con amplias mejoras metalicas, incluyendo alas capaces de vuelo sostenido y blindaje disenado para resistir el combate a gran altitud. He said he used to be an ordinary man, who liked to eat ketupat before eid, he ate ketupat during the fasting month, and showed it to his friends. And one day as he showed her off suddenly, cursed by the ketupat hermit who was angry with her, and transformed herself, into a ghost ketupat. Oh, it's scary!
lyrics_spanish: Ketupat Kepat Prekupat Kupat Kepet Kepot. Es un fantasma de ketupat que proviene de la isla de Java, en el distrito de Krepot Pick Kloot. Vagaba de noche por el bosque. Dijo que solia ser un hombre comun, al que le gustaba comer ketupat antes del Eid, que lo comia durante el mes de ayuno y se lo mostraba a sus amigos. Un dia, mientras la mostraba, de repente, el ermitano de ketupat, enojado con ella, la maldijo y se transformo en un fantasma de ketupat. ¡Que miedo!
personality_english: His face is glowing, and he carries a hammer. He also has a brother - Ini adalah adik dari Ketupat Kepat Prekupat. HRTHR is friend with him.
personality_spanish: Su rostro brilla y lleva un martillo. Tambien tiene un hermano, el hermano menor de Ketupat Kepat Prekupat. HRTHR es amigo suyo.
history_english: Ketupat Kepat Prekupat is a figure in the form of an anthropomorphic Ketupat, a traditional Indonesian rice cake, with limbs and a face.
history_spanish: Ketupat Kepat Prekupat es una figura en forma de un Ketupat antropomorfico, un pastel de arroz tradicional de Indonesia, con extremidades y cara.

name: Ketchuru and Musturu
lyrics_italian: Ketchuru e Musturu. Sono delle strane anomalie, ma allo stesso tempo sono degli incubi in cucina. Erano persone normali, ma una sera volevano mangiare degli hot dog. Uno di loro preparo il barbecue e l'altro preparo ketchup e senape. Il ragazzo, mentre preparava la salsa, fischio una canzone terribile, che fece rovesciare la salsa sugli hot dog e i due ragazzi li mangiarono. Dopo aver finito di mangiare, i due ragazzi iniziarono a provare strane sensazioni, finche all'improvviso si trasformarono in ketchup e senape. Eeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee! Condividilo con i tuoi amici amanti degli hot dog!
lyrics_english: Ketchuru and Musturu. They are very strange anomalies, but at the same time, they are kitchen nightmares. They used to be normal people, but one night, they wanted to eat hot dogs. One of them prepared a barbecue, and the other prepared ketchup and mustard. The boy, while making the sauce, whistled a terrible song, which caused the sauce to spill on the hot dogs and the two boys ate them. After finishing eating, the two boys began to feel strange sensations, until suddenly, they turned into ketchup and mustard. Eek! How scary... Share this with your friends who love hot dogs!
lyrics_spanish: Ketchuru y Musturu. Son anomalias muy extranas, pero a la vez, son pesadillas de cocina. Solian ser personas normales, pero una noche, quisieron comer perritos calientes. Uno preparo la barbacoa y el otro, ketchup y mostaza. El chico, mientras preparaba la salsa, silbo una cancion horrible, que hizo que la salsa se derramara sobre los perritos calientes y los dos chicos se los comieron. Despues de terminar de comer, los dos chicos comenzaron a sentir sensaciones extranas, hasta que de repente, se convirtieron en ketchup y mostaza. ¡Eeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee! ¡Comparte esto con tus amigos amantes de los perritos calientes!
personality_english: Ketchuru and Musturu are two persons, shown as mustard and ketchup bottles, both with limbs. The mustard bottle is sad, while the ketchup bottle is happy.
personality_spanish: Ketchuru y Musturu son dos personas, representadas como botellas de mostaza y ketchup, ambas con extremidades. La botella de mostaza esta triste, mientras que la de ketchup esta feliz.
history_english: Ketchuru and Musturu are an Indonesian Brainrot originally made by @SpyderSammy for the new Steal a Brainrot update. Their video was made by @brainrotmaster900.
history_spanish: Ketchuru y Musturu son dos Brainrot indonesios creados originalmente por @SpyderSammy para la nueva actualizacion "Roba un Brainrot". Su video fue creado por @brainrotmaster900.
